There is a huge spike in the value of the unregulated cryptocurrencies, which are mined using secret algorithms based on the blockchain technologies..
`____ `_ ` `___ `____ `_ `__ `____ `_ `__ `__________ `________________ `____ `__ `____ `____ `_____ `_________ `____ `_ `__ `_________ `_____________ 
According to Forbes, the average 2017 price change of Bitcoin, Ethereum and XRP, three of the most common cryptocurrencies, is a whopping 14,409 per cent. As per the publication, there are now nearly 1,500 cryptoassets in existence, valued at an aggregate USD 550 billion, up 31 times since the beginning of 2017..
